{"title":"Astronomy Photographer of the Year for 2024","link":"https://kottke.org/24/09/astronomy-photographer-of-the-year-for-2024","date":1727190805000,"content":"\n        <p><img src=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/astro-photo-year-2024-01.jpg\" srcset=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=500,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/astro-photo-year-2024-01.jpg 500w, /cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/astro-photo-year-2024-01.jpg 1200w\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1300\" height=\"1670\" alt=\"photo of the ISS transiting the Sun\" /></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/astro-photo-year-2024-02.jpg\" srcset=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=500,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/astro-photo-year-2024-02.jpg 500w, /cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/astro-photo-year-2024-02.jpg 1200w\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1300\" height=\"791\" alt=\"comparision of maximum solar activity with minimum solar activity\" /></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/astro-photo-year-2024-03.jpg\" srcset=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=500,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/astro-photo-year-2024-03.jpg 500w, /cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/astro-photo-year-2024-03.jpg 1200w\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1300\" height=\"732\" alt=\"several stacked images of the Sun during an annular eclipse\" /></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/astro-photo-year-2024-04.jpg\" srcset=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=500,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/astro-photo-year-2024-04.jpg 500w, /cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/ima